coin%20reserve%20and%20digital%20asset%20stockpile.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20reserve%20will%20use%20bitcoin%20and%20other%20digital%20assets%20from%20federal%20asset%20forfeiture%20proceedings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump's%20move%20contrasts%20with%20his%20past%20crypto%20skepticism.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20inked%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F03%2Festablishment-of-the-strategic-bitcoin-reserveand-united-states-digital-asset-stockpile%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20strategic%20bitcoin%20reserve%20and%20a%20digital%20asset%20stockpile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bitcoin%20reserve%20would%20be%20funded%20with%20bitcoin%20owned%20by%20the%20federal%20government%20that%20was%20forfeited%20as%20part%20of%20criminal%20or%20civil%20asset%20proceedings%2C%20according%20to%20the%20executive%20order%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20was%20first%20announced%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdavidsacks47%2Fstatus%2F1897802280738734236%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20entrepreneur%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-leaders-react-donald-trump-winning-election-silicon-valley-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDavid%20Sacks%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20is%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20crypto%20czar%20at%20the%20White%20House.%20He%20said%20that%20because%20of%20the%20way%20the%20reserve%20is%20funded%2C%20creating%20it%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20cost%20taxpayers%20a%20dime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Secretaries%20of%20Treasury%20and%20Commerce%20can%20develop%20%26quot%3Bbudget-neutral%26quot%3B%20strategies%20for%20acquiring%20additional%20bitcoin%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20there%20are%20no%20incremental%20costs%20on%20American%20taxpayers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20executive%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20there%20is%20a%20fixed%20supply%20of%20BTC%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strategic%20advantage%20to%20being%20among%20the%20first%20nations%20to%20create%20a%20strategic%20bitcoin%20reserve%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20executive%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20US%20government%20currently%20holds%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20amount%26quot%3B%20of%20bitcoin%2C%20but%20has%20not%20implemented%20a%20policy%20to%20maximize%20the%20cryptocurrency's%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20position%20as%20a%20unique%20store%20of%20value%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20global%20financial%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20as%20it%20is%20in%20our%20country's%20interest%20to%20thoughtfully%20manage%20national%20ownership%20and%20control%20of%20any%20other%20resource%2C%20our%20Nation%20must%20harness%2C%20not%20limit%2C%20the%20power%20of%20digital%20assets%20for%20our%20prosperity%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Ffact-sheets%2F2025%2F03%2Ffact-sheet-president-donald-j-trump-establishes-the-strategic-bitcoin-reserve-and-u-s-digital-asset-stockpile%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%20added%20in%20a%20fact%20sheet%20that%20premature%20sales%20of%20bitcoin%20have%20%26quot%3Bcost%20US%20taxpayers%20over%20%2417%20billion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20affirmative%20steps%20to%20centralize%20ownership%2C%20control%2C%20and%20management%20of%20these%20assets%20within%20the%20Federal%20government%20will%20ensure%20proper%20oversight%2C%20accurate%20tracking%2C%20and%20a%20cohesive%20approach%20to%20managing%20the%20government's%20cryptocurrency%20holdings%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESacks%20said%20the%20US%20government%20owns%20an%20estimated%20200%2C000%20bitcoins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Reserve%20is%20like%20a%20digital%20Fort%20Knox%20for%20the%20cryptocurrency%20often%20called%20'digital%20gold%2C'%26quot%3B%20Sacks%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBitcoin%20was%20trading%20around%20%2487%2C500%20at%209%3A49%E2%80%AF%20p.m.%20ET.%20It%20was%20flat%20over%201%20hour%20and%204.4%25%20down%20over%2024%20hours.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-price-prediction-btc-bear-market-outlook-options-trading-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecryptocurrency%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20under%20pressure%20recently%20on%20broader%20risk-off%20sentiment.%20Bitcoin%20is%20still%20higher%20than%20on%20election%20day%2C%20when%20the%20price%20was%20around%20%2468%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20will%20also%20establish%20a%20digital%20asset%20stockpile%20made%20up%20of%20other%20digital%20assets%20owned%20by%20the%20Treasury%20Department%20that%20were%20forfeited%20in%20criminal%20or%20civil%20asset%20forfeiture%20proceedings%2C%20according%20to%20the%20executive%20order.%20There%20are%20also%20no%20plans%20to%20acquire%20additional%20assets%20beyond%20those%20from%20forfeiture%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%20presidential%20campaign%2C%20Trump%20took%20a%20tough%20stance%20on%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1149472282584072192%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edescribed%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20digital%20assets%20as%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20volatile%20and%20based%20on%20thin%20air%26quot%3B%20and%20highlighted%20their%20role%20in%20the%20drug%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20embraced%20crypto%20in%20his%20last%20presidential%20campaign%20and%20called%20himself%20the%20%26quot%3Bcrypto%20president.%26quot%3B%20The%20new%20administration%20is%20ending%20Biden-era%20investigations%20into%20cryptocurrency-associated%20companies%2C%20among%20other%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-strategic