26quot%3B%20Trump%20posted%20on%20his%20social%20media%20platform%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president's%20message%20represents%20the%20first%20move%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20power%20accorded%20to%20Musk%2C%20as%20his%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE)%20works%20toward%20gutting%20federal%20staffing%20and%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20later%2C%20directly%20asked%20by%20reporters%20whether%20DOGE%20and%20Musk%20are%20moving%20too%20fast%2C%20Trump%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20I%20think%20they've%20done%20an%20amazing%20job.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Musk%20is%20not%20the%20formal%20administrator%20of%20DOGE%2C%20the%20SpaceX%20and%20Tesla%20CEO%20is%20nonetheless%20directing%20operations%20and%20even%20attended%20the%20first%20cabinet%20meeting%20of%20Trump's%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20body's%20cost-cutting%20campaign%20has%20faced%20increasing%20resistance%20on%20multiple%20fronts%2C%20however%2C%20including%20court%20rulings%20and%20some%20pressure%20from%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDOGE%20has%20been%20an%20incredible%20success%2C%20and%20now%20that%20we%20have%20my%20Cabinet%20in%20place%2C%20I%20have%20instructed%20the%20Secretaries%20and%20Leadership%20to%20work%20with%20DOGE%20on%20Cost%20Cutting%20measures%20and%20Staffing%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20Secretaries%20learn%20about%2C%20and%20understand%2C%20the%20people%20working%20for%20the%20various%20Departments%2C%20they%20can%20be%20very%20precise%20as%20to%20who%20will%20remain%2C%20and%20who%20will%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20confirmed%20reports%20in%20the%20US%20media%20that%20he%20had%20convened%20his%20cabinet%20in%20person%20on%20Thursday%20to%20deliver%20the%20message%20that%20they%2C%20not%20Musk%2C%20were%20in%20charge%20of%20their%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20told%20his%20team%2C%20with%20Musk%20in%20the%20room%20and%20on%20board%2C%20that%20the%20tech%20billionaire%20and%20top%20donor%20was%20authorized%20to%20recommend%20firings%20and%20other%20cuts%20but%20not%20to%20enforce%20them%2C%20according%20to%20Politico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20important%20that%20we%20cut%20levels%20down%20to%20where%20they%20should%20be%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20important%20to%20keep%20the%20best%20and%20most%20productive%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20president%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20follow-up%20cabinet%20meetings%20on%20DOGE%20would%20come%20every%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20fired%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20message%20came%20with%20the%20administration%20having%20fired%20or%20threatened%20to%20axe%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20workers%20from%20numerous%20federal%20agencies%20as%20it%20pursues%20cost%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20two%20million%20federal%20employees%20received%20demands%20from%20the%20US%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20(OPM)%20--%20the%20government's%20human%20resources%20department%20--%20and%20Musk%20himself%20that%20they%20account%20for%20the%20work%20they%20have%20been%20doing%20in%20a%20bullet%20pointed%20memo%20or%20face%20the%20sack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELabor%20groups%20quickly%20opposed%20the%20request%2C%20with%20the%20largest%20federal%20employee%20union%2C%20the%20American%20Federation%20of%20Government%20Employees%20(AFGE)%2C%20vowing%20to%20challenge%20any%20unlawful%20terminations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20recent%20polls%20indicate%20that%20most%20Americans%20disapprove%20of%20the%20disruption%20to%20the%20nationwide%20federal%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20lawsuits%20against%20Musk's%20threats%20or%20demands%20have%20yielded%20mixed%20results%2C%20with%20some%20requests%20for%20immediate%20halts%20to%20his%20executive%20orders%20being%20denied%20by%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitico%20said%20Musk%20--%20who%20had%20meetings%20with%20Republican%20lawmakers%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20reassure%20them%20over%20criticism%20of%20DOGE%20--%20acknowledged%20in%20front%20of%20the%20cabinet%20that%20the%20task%20force%20had%20made%20missteps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20a%20third%20of%20DOGE%20staffers%20had%20resigned%20in%20protest%20over%20its%20methods%20by%20the%20end%20of%20February%2C%20saying%20they%20would%20not%20push%20through%20demanded%20changes%20that%20put%20the%20country%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20swore%20to%20serve%20the%20American%20people%20and%20uphold%20our%20oath%20to%20the%20Constitution%20across%20presidential%20administrations%2C%26quot%3B%2021%20staffers%20of%20DOGE%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%2C%20seen%20by%20AFP%2C%20to%20White%20House%20chief%20of%20staff%20Susan%20Wiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20it%20has%20become%20clear%20that%20we%20can%20no%20longer%20honor%20those%20commitments%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cuts%20have%20even%20sparked%20criticism%20from%20the%20normally%20staunchly-loyal%20Senate%20Republicans%2C%20whose%20leader%20John%20Thune%20preempted%20Trump%20by%20telling%20CNN%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20cabinet%20officials%20should%20retain%20the%20full%20control%20of%20personnel%20decisions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741314720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F1v666rno_elon-musk-donald-trump_625x300_07_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-says-elon-musk-should-use-scalpel-not-hatchet-in-doge-government-cuts-7866726%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump's%20message%20represents%20the%20first%20move%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20power%20accorded%20to%20Elon%20Musk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-tr