0a%20connection%20to%20the%20previous%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%20this%20happened%20last%20time%20too%2C%20so%20we've%20got%20some%20practice%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20SpaceX%20spokesperson%20Dan%20Huot%20said%20on%20the%20live%20stream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20whether%20the%20explosion%20was%20caused%20by%20SpaceX's%20automated%20flight%20termination%20system%2C%20which%20triggers%20when%20something%20on%20the%20rocket%20goes%20wrong.%20The%20ship%20showed%20signs%20of%20failure%20before%20its%20explosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20described%20the%20failure%20in%20technical%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20Starship's%20ascent%20burn%2C%20the%20vehicle%20experienced%20a%20rapid%20unscheduled%20disassembly%20and%20contact%20was%20lost%2C%26quot%3B%20SpaceX%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BOur%20team%20immediately%20began%20coordination%20with%20safety%20officials%20to%20implement%20pre-planned%20contingency%20responses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Starship%20failure%20in%20January%20ended%20eight%20minutes%20into%20flight%20when%20the%20rocket%20exploded%2C%20raining%20debris%20over%20Caribbean%20islands%20and%20causing%20minor%20damage%20to%20a%20car%20in%20the%20Turks%20and%20Caicos%20Islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA%2C%20which%20regulates%20private%20rocket%20launches%2C%20said%20its%20investigation%20would%20require%20SpaceX%20to%20examine%20the%20failure's%20cause%20and%20get%20the%20agency's%20sign-off%20before%20Starship%20can%20fly%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA%20last%20month%20approved%20SpaceX's%20launch%20license%20for%20Thursday's%20test%20flight%20while%20its%20investigation%20into%20the%20company's%20previous%20Starship%20failure%20remained%20open.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20FAA%20said%20it%20had%20reviewed%20SpaceX's%20license%20application%20and%20early%20details%20from%20the%20company's%20mishap%20investigation%20before%20determining%20that%20Starship's%20eighth%20flight%20could%20proceed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarship%20was%20aiming%20to%20make%20nearly%20a%20full%20orbit%20around%20Earth%20and%20reenter%20over%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20for%20a%20splashdown%2C%20simulating%20a%20landing%20sequence%20that%20SpaceX%20wants%20to%20soon%20carry%20out%20on%20land%20as%20a%20key%20next%20phase%20of%20the%20rocket's%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741314180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Foj61tq0g_spacex-debris_625x300_07_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-debris-over-bahamas-after-elon-musks-spacex-starship-explodes-in-space-7866569%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SpaceX's%20Starship%20spacecraft%20tumbled%20and%20exploded%20in%20space%20on%20Thursday%20minutes%20after%20lifting%20off%20from%20Texas%2C%20dooming%20an%20attempt%20to%20deploy%20mock%20satellites%20in%20the%20second%20consecutive%20failure%20this%20year%20for%20Elon%20Musk's%20Mars%20rocket%20program.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-debris-over-bahamas-after-elon-musks-spacex-starship-explodes-in-space-7866569%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20on%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%E2%80%99%20hair%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741313997000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118772464%2Cimgsize-567537.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fetimes%2Ftrending%2Fdonald-trump-comments-on-sunita-williams-hair-says-people-who-are-struck-in-space-should-love-each-other%2Farticleshow%2F118772463.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20assured%20stranded%20astronauts%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%20that%20efforts%20are%20underway%20for%20their%20return%2C%20blaming%20Joe%20Biden%20for%20their%20situation.%20Originally%20planned%20as%20an%208-day%20mission%2C%20technical%20faults%20in%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20have%20kept%20them%20in%20space%20since%20June%202024.%20They%20may%20return%20to%20Earth%20in%20March%202025%20aboard%20a%20SpaceX%20vehicle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20LIFESTYLE%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fetimes%2Ftrending%2Fdonald-trump-comments-on-sunita-williams-hair-says-people-who-are-struck-in-space-should-love-each-other%2Farticleshow%2F118772463.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%20Faces%20Another%20Setback%2C%20Starship%20Explodes%20In%20Space%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%20on%20Thursday%20once%20again%20lost%20the%20upper%20stage%20of%20its%20massive%20Starship%20rocket%20in%20a%20fiery%20explosion%2C%20even%20as%20the%20booster%20was%20successfully%20caught%20in%20its%20latest%20orbital%20test%20--%20a%20near%20replay%20of%20the%20previous%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinutes%20after%20liftoff%20and%20booster%20separation%2C%20a%20live%20video%20feed%20showed%20the%20upper%20stage%20tumbling%20uncontrollably%20before%20the%20signal%20abruptly%20cut%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDramatic%20footage%20circulating%20online%20captured%20red-hot%20debris%20raining%20down%20over%20the%20Bahamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20confirm%20we%20did%20lose%20contact%20with%20the%20ship.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20happened%20last%20time%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20SpaceX%20spokesman%20Dan%20Huot%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20January's%20flight%2C%20which%20also%20ended%20with%20the%20upper%20stage%20disintegrating%20over%20the%20Caribbean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fallout%20was%20felt%20immediately%20in%20US%20airspace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20(FAA)%20briefly%20activated%20a%20%26quot%3Bdebris%20response%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20delaying%20flights%20from%20airports%20stretching%20from%20Newark%20and%20Philadelphia%20to%20Miami.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20confirmed%20SpaceX%20will%20be%20required%20to%20conduct%20a%20mishap%20investigation%20before%20it%20can%20fly%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20setback%2C%20SpaceX's%20%26quot%3Bfail%20fast%2C%20learn%20fast%26quot%3B%20approach%20has%20helped%20it%20become%20the%20world's%20dominant%20launch%20services%20provider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Musk's%20status%20as%20one%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20closest%20advisors%20and%20his%20influence%20over%20federal%20regulators%20are%20raising%20concerns%20about%20potential%20conflicts%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEighth%20Starship%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarship%20--%20the%20world's%20largest%20and%20most%20powerful%20rocket%20--%20lifted%20off%20from%20SpaceX's%20Starbase%20facility%20in%20Boca%20Chica%2C%20Texas%2C%20shortly%20after%205%3A30%20pm%20(2330%20GMT).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20marked%20its%20eighth%20uncrewed%20orbital%20test%2C%20after%20earlier%20launch%20attempts%20were%20scrubbed%20on%20Monday%20and%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20upper%20stage%20was%20lost%20for%20a%20second%20consecutive%20flight%2C%20SpaceX%20successfully%20recovered%20the%20Super%20Heavy%20booster%2C%20catching%20it%20with%20the%20launch%20tower's%20mechanical%20%26quot%3Bchopstick%26quot%3B%20arms%20for%20the%20third%20time%20--%20an%20impressive%20feat%20of%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2040%20minutes%20after%20launch%2C%20SpaceX%20ended%20its%20livestream%20without%20providing%20further%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStanding%20403%20feet%20(123%20meters)%20tall%20--%20about%20100%20feet%20taller%20than%20the%20Statue%20of%