30pm%20ET%20(1730%20UTC).%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1kmUECWgqj%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1kmUECWgqj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NASA%20(%40NASA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNASA%2Fstatus%2F1897754174260974019%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%206%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntuitive%20Machines'%20share%20price%20tumbled%2020%20percent%20in%20afternoon%20trading.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20suggested%20that%2C%20as%20in%20its%20previous%20mission%2C%20issues%20with%20Athena's%20laser%20altimeters%2C%20which%20provide%20altitude%20and%20velocity%20readings%2C%20may%20have%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20suboptimal%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAthena%2C%20like%20its%20predecessor%20Odysseus%2C%20has%20a%20tall%2C%20slender%20build.%20At%2015.6%20feet%20(4.8%20meters)%20--%20the%20height%20of%20a%20giraffe%20--%20it%20had%20raised%20stability%20concerns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Altemus%20emphasized%20that%20the%20lander's%20weight%20distribution%20kept%20the%20center%20of%20gravity%20low%2C%20and%20Intuitive%20Machines%20remains%20confident%20in%20its%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpectations%20were%20high%20after%20Texas%20rival%20Firefly%20Aerospace%20successfully%20landed%20its%20Blue%20Ghost%20lander%20on%20the%20Moon%20on%20Sunday%20on%20its%20first%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECutting-edge%20technologies%20at%20stake%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20missions%20are%20part%20of%20NASA's%20%242.6%20billion%20Commercial%20Lunar%20Payload%20Services%20(CLPS)%20program%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20leverage%20private%20industry%20to%20reduce%20costs%20and%20support%20Artemis%2C%20NASA's%20effort%20to%20return%20astronauts%20to%20the%20Moon%20and%20eventually%20to%20reach%20Mars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAthena%20carries%20an%20ice-drilling%20experiment%2C%20a%204G%20cellular%20network%20test%2C%20three%20rovers%2C%20and%20a%20unique%20hopping