r%20panels%20could%20not%20generate%20enough%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAthena%20launched%20last%20Wednesday%20aboard%20a%20SpaceX%20Falcon%209%20rocket%2C%20which%20also%20carried%20NASA's%20Lunar%20Trailblazer%20probe%2C%20a%20spacecraft%20designed%20to%20map%20the%20Moon's%20water%20distribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20ground%20controllers%20have%20been%20struggling%20to%20re-establish%20contact%20with%20Trailblazer%2C%20adding%20to%20NASA's%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20missions%20come%20at%20a%20delicate%20time%20for%20NASA%2C%20amid%20speculation%20that%20the%20agency%20may%20scale%20back%20or%20even%20cancel%20the%20crewed%20Moon%20missions%20in%20favor%20of%20prioritizing%20Mars%2C%20a%20goal%20championed%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20billionaire%20advisor%20and%20SpaceX%20owner%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741312800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fm2pk4rj_-athena_625x300_07_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprivate-us-spaceship-athena-by-intuitive-machines-lands-near-moons-south-pole-but-awkwardly-7866607%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Intuitive%20Machines%20made%20history%20in%202024%20as%20the%20first%20private%20firm%20to%20place%20a%20spaceship%20on%20Earth's%20nearest%20neighbor%2C%20though%20the%20moment%20was%20marred%20by%20Odysseus%20toppling%20over%20upon%20touchdown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprivate-us-spaceship-athena-by-intuitive-machines-lands-near-moons-south-pole-but-awkwardly-7866607%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20stocks%20to%20buy%20today%3A%20Stock%20recommendations%20for%20March%2