E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20approach%20he%20has%20been%20following%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years%20or%20so.%20It%20started%20around%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20India%2C%20and%20he%20has%20been%20sticking%20to%20that%20formula.%20He%20has%20had%20some%20success%2C%20though%20perhaps%20not%20as%20much%20as%20his%20talent%20should%20warrant.%20He%20is%20an%20incredibly%20talented%20player%20with%20a%20range%20of%20shots%20that%20not%20many%20others%20in%20the%20game%20possess%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fstory%2Fchampions-trophy-sunil-gavaskar-on-rohit-sharma-intent-gautam-gambhir-presser-2689553-2025-03-05%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20from%20an%20aesthetic%20point%20of%20view%2C%20from%20a%20crowd-pleasing%20perspective%2C%20I%20am%20not%20speaking%20from%20the%20team's%20point%20of%20view.%20He%20bats%20for%20even%2025%20overs%2C%20India%20will%20be%20around%20180-200.%20Imagine%20if%20they%20have%20lost%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20wickets%20by%20then%3B%20just%20think%20what%20they%20could%20do-they%20could%20reach%20350%20or%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20Rohit%20should%20not%20happy%20scoring%2025-30%20runs%20and%20his%20impact%20for%20his%20side%20should%20be%20far%20greater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20also%20needs%20to%20give%20it%20some%20thought.%20It's%20one%20thing%20to%20go%20out%20and%20play%20aggressively%2C%20but%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20discretion%20somewhere%20to%20give%20himself%20the%20chance%20to%20bat%20for%2025-30%20overs.%20If%20he%20does%20that%2C%20he%20takes%20the%20game%20away%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20kind%20of%20impact%20is%20match-winning.%20And%20I%20think%2C%20as%20a%20batter%2C%20are%20you%20happy%20with%20scoring%2025-30%20runs%3F%20You%20shouldn't%20be!%20So%20that%20is%20what%20I%20would%20say%20to%20him%3A%20your%20impact%20on%20the%20team%20will%20be%20even%20greater%20if%20you%20bat%20for%2025%20overs%20instead%20of%20just%20seven%2C%20eight%2C%20or%20nine%20overs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741311900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F4ch7a5v8_sc_625x300_06_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fare-you-happy-scoring-25-30-runs-sunil-gavaskar-blasts-gautam-gambhirs-rohit-sharma-take-7859158%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Legendary%20India%20batter%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20advised%20Rohit%20Sharma%20to%20bat%20for%20longer%20periods%20of%20time%20instead%20of%20just%20concentrating%20on%20providing%20the%20team%20with%20a%20quick%20start.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fare-you-happy-scoring-25-30-runs-sunil-gavaskar-blasts-gautam-gambhirs-rohit-sharma-take-7859158%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zeenat%20reveals%20she%20regrets%20missing%20out%20on%20'Amar%20Akbar%20Anthony'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741311674000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118772229%2Cimgsize-70118.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fzeenat-aman-reveals-she-regrets-missing-out-on-amar-akbar-anthony-heres-why-she-couldnt-do-it-i-dont-regret-holding-my-ground%2Farticleshow%2F118772237.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118772237.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EZeenat%20Aman%20was%20offered%20a%20role%20in%20'Amar%20Akbar%20Anthony'%2C%20and%20she%20confesses%20that%20she%20regrets%20missing%20out%20on%20the%20role.%20The%20film%20starred%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20Rishi%20Kapoor%2C%20Vinod%20Khanna%2C%20Parveen%20Babi%2C%20Neetu%20Kapoor%20and%20Shabana%20Azmi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fzeenat-aman-reveals-she-regrets-missing-out-on-amar-akbar-anthony-heres-why-she-couldnt-do-it-i-dont-regret-holding-my-ground%2Farticleshow%2F118772237.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%20Suggests%20Ice%20May%20Exist%20On%20Moon%20At%20More%20Locations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIce%20could%20be%20present%20at%20more%20locations%20right%20beneath%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20at%20the%20poles%20than%20previously%20thought%2C%20a%20study%20of%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20has%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarge%2C%20yet%20highly%20local%2C%20changes%20in%20surface%20temperatures%20can%20directly%20affect%20the%20forming%20of%20ice%2C%20and%20looking%20into%20these%20ice%20particles%20can%20reveal%20%26quot%3Bdifferent%20stories%20about%20their%20origin%20and%20history%26quot%3B%2C%20lead%20author%2C%20Durga%20Prasad%20Karanam%2C%20Faculty%2C%20Physical%20Research%20Laboratory%2C%20Ahmedabad%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20also%20tell%20us%20about%20how%20ice%20accumulated%20and%20moved%20through%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20over%20time%2C%20which%20can%20provide%20insights%20into%20the%20natural%20satellite's%20early%20geologic%20processes%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20findings%20are%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Communications%20Earth%20and%20Environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%2C%20launched%20by%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%20achieved%20a%20soft%20landing%20near%20the%20Moon's%20south%20pole%20on%20August%2023%2C%202023.%20The%20landing%20site%20was%20named%20the%20'Shiv%20Shakti%20Point'%20three%20days%20later%20on%20August%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20study%2C%20the%20researchers%20analysed%20temperatures%20measured%20at%20and%20to%20a%20depth%20of%2010%20centimetres%20beneath%20the%20lunar%20surface.%20Measurements%20were%20taken%20by%20the%20'ChaSTE'%20probe%20on-board%20the%20Chandrayaan-3's%20Vikram%20lander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lander%20touched%20down%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20Moon's%20south%20pole%20region%2C%20about%2069%20degrees%20south%20latitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20landing%20site%20--%20%26quot%3Ba%20Sun-facing%20slope%20angled%20at%20six%20degrees%26quot%3B%20--%20the%20authors%20found%20that%20temperatures%20peaked%20at%20about%2082%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%20dropped%20to%20-170%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20barely%20a%20metre%20away%20from%20the%20landing%20point%20--%20a%20flat%20surface%20--%20temperatures%20peaked%20at%20about%2060%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20slight%20slope%20resulted%20in%20an%20increased%20solar%20radiation%20at%20the%20ChaSTE%20penetration%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Karanam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20team%20developed%20a%20model%20of%20how%20slope%20angle%20can%20affect%20surface%20temperature%20at%20a%20high%20lunar%20latitude%2C%20such%20as%20the%20latitude%20of%20the%20landing%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20indicated%20that%2C%20for%20slopes%20facing%20away%20from%20the%20Sun%20and%20towards%20the%20Moon's%20nearest%20pole%2C%20a%20slope%20inclined%20at%20an%20angle%20greater%20than%2014%20degrees%20may%20be%20cool%20enough%20for%20ice%20to%20accumulate%20close%20to%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slope%20conditions%20suggested%20by%20the%20model%20were%20found%20to%20be%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20landing%20points%2C%20proposed%20for%20NASA's%20manned%20mission%20to%20the%20Moon's%20south%20pole%20--%20the%20'Artemis'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%2C%20therefore%2C%20suggested%20that%20potentially%2C%20there%20could%20be%20multiple%20places%20on%20the%20Moon%20where%20ice%20can%20form%20and%20be%20accessed%20more%20easily%20than%20previously%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20PTI's%20question%20on%20the%20chances%20of%20ice%20turning%20into%20water%20on%20the%20Moon%2C%20Karanam%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWater%20in%20liquid%20form%20cannot%20exist%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%20because%20of%20(an)%20ultra-high%20vacuum.%20Therefore%2C%20ice%20cannot%20transform%20into%20liquid%2C%20but%20would%20rather%20sublimate%20to%20vapour%20form.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAs%20of%20the%20present%20understanding%2C%20Moon%20might%20not%20have%20had%20habitable%20conditions%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Karanam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20ice%20is%20a%20potential%20resource%20for%20future%20on-site%20exploration%20and%20habitability%20of%20the%20Moon%2C%20and%20that%20more%20measurements%2C%20such%20as%20those%20from%20ChaSTE%2C%20are%20needed%20to%20gain%20a%20comprehensive%20picture%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechniques%20and%20strategies%20need%20to%20be%20developed%20for%20extraction%20and%20usage%20of%20ice%20for%20long%20term%20sustainability%20on%20the%20Moon%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lead%20author%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BChaSTE%20findings%20not%20only%20indicate%20fine%20scale%20spatial%20variability%20in%20regolith%20temperatures%20but%20also%20suggest%20that%20high-latitude%20regions%20are%20potential%20sites%20for%20scouting%20water-ice%2C%20resource%20prospecting%20and%20habitation.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSuch%20sites%20are%20not%20only%20scientifically%20interesting%20but%20also%20pose%20less%20technical%20challenges%20for%20exploration%20in%20comparison%20with%20regions%20closer%20to%20the%20poles%20of%20the%20Moon%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741311660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F9hvmgn28_moon-generic_625x300_29_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fchandrayaan-3-data-suggests-says-ice-may-exist-on-moon-at-more-locations-than-previously-thought-7864373%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ice%20could%20be%20present%20at%20more%20locations%20right%20beneath%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20at%20the%20poles%20than%20previously%20thought%2C%20a%20study%20of%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20has%20suggested.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fchandrayaan-3-data-suggests-says-ice-may-exist-on-moon-at-more-locations-than-previously-thought-7864373%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20SpaceX%20Starship%20explodes%20mid-air%2C%20fiery%20debris%20streaks%20across%20Bahamas%20sky%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741311230000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118772431%2Cimgsize-3463296.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-spacex-starship-explodes-mid-air-fiery-debris-streaks-across-florida-bahamas-sky%2Farticleshow%2F118772171.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-spacex-starship-explodes-mid-air-fiery-debris-streaks-across-florida-bahamas-sky%2Farticleshow%2F118772171.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20SpaceX%20Starship%20explodes%20mid-air%2C%20fiery%20debris%20streaks%20across%20Florida-Bahamas%20sky%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741311230000%2C%2