%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20are%20chairs%20and%20tables%20where%20customers%20can%20sit%20while%20waiting%20for%20their%20laundry%20to%20be%20done.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd2fdd91-7346-4196-89f1-4d7fb34ea588%5C%22%3ETrusting%20her%20gut%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHangout%20Laundry%20is%20tucked%20away%20in%20the%20corner%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsee-inside-public-housing-singapore-hdb-million-dollars-blue-zone-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20housing%20apartment%20block.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%20has%20been%20marketing%20the%20laundromat%20since%20it%20doesn't%20receive%20a%20lot%20of%20foot%20traffic%3B%20the%20nearest%20subway%20station%20is%20about%20a%2015-minute%20walk%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20on%20the%20laundromat's%20website%20has%20been%20optimized%20for%20search%20engines%2C%20Low%20said.%20That%2C%20coupled%20with%20getting%20their%20regulars%20to%20leave%20reviews%2C%20has%20helped%20boost%20their%20visibility%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223798%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20token%20machine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c1255769253ccddf97ddf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222848%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20laundromat%20uses%20a%20token%20system.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20ultimately%2C%20it's%20the%20experience%20that%20will%20keep%20customers%20coming%20back%20%E2%80%94%20something%20they%20feel%20is%20enhanced%20through%20social%20interaction.%20That's%20why%20Low%20and%20her%20husband%20take%20turns%20coming%20in%20almost%20every%20day%20to%20get%20to%20know%20their%20customers%20and%20listen%20to%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELow%20said%20trusting%20her%20gut%20also%20paid%20off.%20For%20instance%2C%20she%20was%20told%20it%20w