t%20turmoil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20halt%20--%20which%20will%20last%20until%20April%202%20--%20offers%20relief%20to%20automakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20auto%20sector%2C%20parts%20cross%20North%20American%20borders%20multiple%20times%20during%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20talks%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Three%26quot%3B%20US%20automakers%20--%20Stellantis%2C%20Ford%20and%20General%20Motors%20--%20Washington%20initially%20announced%20a%20one-month%20exemption%20on%20autos%20coming%20through%20the%20United%20States-Mexico-Canada%20Agreement%20(USMCA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20official%20told%20reporters%20that%20about%2062%20percent%20of%20Canadian%20imports%20will%20still%20face%20the%20new%20tariffs%2C%20although%20much%20of%20these%20are%20energy%20products%20hit%20by%20a%20lower%20rate%20of%2010%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20half%20of%20Mexican%20imports%20come%20through%20the%20USMCA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20moves%20make%20conditions%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20more%20favorable%20for%20our%20American%20car%20manufacturers%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20Trump's%20decision%2C%20Canadian%20Finance%20Minister%20Dominic%20LeBlanc%20wrote%20on%20X%20that%20his%20country%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20proceed%20with%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20tariffs%20on%20%24125B%20of%20US%20products%20until%20April%202nd%2C%20while%20we%20continue%20to%20work%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20all%20tariffs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20Thursday%20that%20more%20tariffs%20would%20come%20on%20April%202%2C%20adding%20they%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%20in%20nature.%26quot%3B%20He%20had%20earlier%20vowed%20reciprocal%20levies%20to%20remedy%20practices%20Washington%20deems%20unfair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20Canadian%20and%20Mexican%20goods%20could%20still%20face%20levies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20president%20also%20said%20he%20would%20not%20modify%20broad%20tariffs%20for%20steel%20and%20aluminum%20imports%2C%20which%20are%20due%20to%20take%20effect%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20stock%20markets%20slumped%20again%20Thursday%20despite%20Trump's%20partial%20tariff%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Tremendous%20progress'%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20told%20reporters%20Thursday%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20that%20he%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20good%20conversation%26quot%3B%20with%20Mexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20%26quot%3Btremendous%20progress%26quot%3B%20on%20both%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20drugs%20coming%20into%20the%20United%20States%20--%20both%20reasons%20that%20Washington%20cited%20in%20imposing%20levies%20on%20Mexico%2C%20Canada%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20stood%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20simmering%20tensions%20with%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20said%20Thursday%20that%20Ottawa%20will%20remain%20in%20a%20trade%20war%20with%20Washington%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20foreseeable%20future%26quot%3B%20even%20if%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bbreaks%20for%20certain%20sectors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20goal%20remains%20to%20get%20these%20tariffs%2C%20all%20tariffs%20removed%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20contributes%20less%20than%20one%20percent%20of%20fentanyl%20to%20the%20illicit%20US%20supply%2C%20according%20to%20Canadian%20and%20US%20government%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20pushed%20back%20on%20US%20allegations%20of%20its%20role%20in%20the%20fentanyl%20supply%20chain%2C%20calling%20this%20a%20domestic%20issue%20that%20tariffs%20will%20not%20resolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Economic%20reality'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Scott%20Lincicome%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20general%20economics%20at%20the%20Cato%20Institute%2C%20Trump's%20easing%20of%20tariffs%20was%