3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20gonna%20confirm%20or%20deny%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Sen.%20Eric%20Schmitt%20of%20Missouri%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI've%20met%20with%20him%20twice%20in%20the%20last%20two%20weeks.%20He's%20been%20very%20accessible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20an%20awareness%20of%20the%20power%20that%20Musk%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20the%20de%20facto%20head%20of%20DOGE%2C%20but%20the%20owner%20of%20what%20may%20be%20the%20world's%20most%20important%20communication%20platform%2C%20X%20%E2%80%94%20holds%20relative%20to%20them.%20And%20some%20of%20them%20don't%20hide%20their%20own%20sense%20of%20awe%20at%20the%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Ted%20Cruz%20did%20not%20confirm%20or%20deny%20that%20Musk%20gave%20out%20his%20number%20on%20Wednesday.%20But%20the%20Texas%20Republican%20said%20he's%20had%20Musk's%20number%20for%20years%20and%20that%20he's%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20friend.%26quot%3B%20When%20asked%20what%20the%20billionaire%20businessman%20is%20like%20over%20text%2C%20Cruz%20launched%20into%20a%20two-and-a-half%20minute-long%20disquisition%20about%20Musk's%20brilliance%20and%20business%20acumen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20assume%20that%20intelligence%20is%20distributed%20on%20a%20bell%20curve%20there%20are%20roughly%208%20billion%20people%20on%20Planet%20Earth%2C%20somebody%20has%20to%20be%20at%20the%20bleeding%20edge%20of%20the%20bell%20curve%2C%20and%20his%20name%20is%20Elon%2C%26quot%3B%20Cruz%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20blessed%20to%20know%20many%20really%20smart%20people.%20I've%20never%20met%20anyone%20remotely%20like%20Elon%20Musk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublican%20Sen.%20Ron%20Johnson%20of%20Wisconsin%20%E2%80%94%20who%20said%20his%20own%20hypothetical%20text%20communication%20with%20Musk%20would%20%26quot%3Bremain%20private%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20he%20and%20his%20colleagues%20were%20being%20coy%20about%20having%20Musk's%20number%20because%20they're%20%26quot%3Bsensitive%20about%20people%20having%20access%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20%26quot%3Babuse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20he%20also%20offered%20some%20unsolicited%20praise%20for%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he's%20a%20remarkable%20individual.%20He's%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20more%20brilliant%2C%20accomplished%2C%20effective%20human%20beings%20ever%20to%20walk%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Earth%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he's%20%26quot%3Bvery%20appreciative%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20he's%20willing%20to%20devote%20his%20very%20expensive%20time%26quot%3B%20to%20DOGE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWednesday's%20lunch%20with%20GOP%20senators%20was%20just%20one%20of%20several%20meetings%20that%20Musk%20has%20had%20with%20congressional%20Republicans%20in%20the%20last%20two%20weeks.%20Later%20that%20day%2C%20he%20met%20with%20a%20larger%20group%20of%20House%20Republicans%2C%20plus%20a%20smaller%20meeting%20with%20the%20Republicans%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-subcommittee-first-hearing-elon-musk-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%20subcommittee%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That's%20on%20top%20of%20a%20meeting%20last%20Thursday%20with%20the%20Senate%20DOGE%20Caucus%20and%20a%20meeting%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20with%20House%20Speaker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-mike-johnson-republican-speaker-house-louisiana-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMike%20Johnson%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20as%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-caucus-subcommittee-congress-too-fast-ideas-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERepublicans%20grow%20anxious%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20congressional%20input%20over%20DOGE's%20spending%20decisions%2C%20with%20some%20urging%20the%20White%20House%20to%20send%20federal%20spending%20cuts%20to%20Congress%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Brecission%26quot%3B%20