i%3EFormer%20Google%20CEO%20Eric%20Schmidt%20co-authored%20a%20paper%20warning%20the%20US%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20an%20AI%20Manhattan%20Project.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20paper%2C%20Schmidt%2C%20Dan%20Hendrycks%2C%20and%20Alexandr%20Wang%20push%20for%20a%20more%20defensive%20approach.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20authors%20suggest%20the%20US%20sabotage%20rival%20projects%2C%20rather%20than%20advance%20the%20AI%20frontier%20alone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20AI%20tech%20say%20an%20AI%20%26quot%3BManhattan%20Project%26quot%3B%20could%20have%20a%20destabalizing%20effect%20on%20the%20US%2C%20rather%20than%20help%20safeguard%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dire%20warning%20came%20from%20former%20Google%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-schmidt-ai-risks-biological-attacks-rogue-states-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEric%20Schmidt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Center%20for%20AI%20Safety%20director%20Dan%20Hendrycks%2C%20and%20Scale%20AI%20CEO%20Alexandr%20Wang.%20They%20coauthored%20a%20policy%20paper%20titled%20%26quot%3BSuperintelligence%20Strategy%26quot%3B%20published%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20paper%2C%20the%20tech%20titans%20urge%20the%20US%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20an%20aggressive%20push%20to%20develop%20superintelligent%20AI%2C%20or%20AGI%2C%20which%20the%20authors%20say%20could%20provoke%20international%20retaliation.%20China%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20%26quot%3Bwould%20not%20sit%20idle%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20US%20worked%20to%20actualize%20AGI%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Brisk%20a%20loss%20of%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20write.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20write%20that%20circumstances%20similar%20to%20the%20nuclear%20arms%20race%20that%20birthed%20the%20Manhattan%20Project%20%E2%80%94%20a%20secretive%20initiative%20that%20ended%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20first%20atom%20bomb%20%E2%80%94%20have%20developed%20around%20the%20AI%20frontier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202024%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20bipartisan%20congressional%20committee%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-us-china-race-ai-manhattan-project-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManhattan%20Project-like%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20program%2C%20dedicated%20to%20pumping%20funds%20into%20initiatives%20that%20could%20help%20the%20US%20beat%20out%20China%20in%20the%20race%20to%20AGI.%20And%20just%20a%20few%20days%20before%20the%20authors%20released%20their%20paper%2C%20US%20Secretary%20of%20Energy%20Chris%20Wright%20said%20the%20country%20is%20already%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20Manhattan%20Project.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Manhattan%20Project%20assumes%20that%20rivals%20will%20acquiesce%20to%20an%20enduring%20imbalance%20or%20omnicide%20rather%20than%20move%20to%20prevent%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20write.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20begins%20as%20a%20push%20for%20a%20superweapon%20and%20global%20control%20risks%20prompting%20hostile%20countermeasures%20and%20escalating%20tensions%2C%20thereby%20undermining%20the%20very%20stability%20the%20strategy%20purports%20to%20secure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20the%20government%20subsidizing%20AI%20advancements%2C%20either%2C%20according%20to%20Schmidt%2C%20Hendrycks%2C%20and%20Wang%20%E2%80%94%20private%20corporations%20are%20developing%20%26quot%3BManhattan%20Projects%26quot%3B%20of%20their%20own.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-demis-hassabis-deepmind-founder-ai-google-nobel-prize-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDemis%20Hassabis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CEO%20of%20Google%20DeepMind%2C%20has%20said%20he%20loses%20sleep%20over%20the%20possibility%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind-ceo-demis-hassabis-anthropic-ceo-ai-pressure-worries-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eending%20up%20like%20Robert%20Oppenheim