%20Hosur%20is%20now%20being%20widely%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%20and%20has%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20all%20four%20adults.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20is%20a%2014-year-old%20girl%20from%20Thimmathur%2C%20a%20small%20village%20in%20the%20Thottamanju%20mountain%20area%20near%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Hosur.%20After%20studying%20till%20Class%207%20in%20a%20local%20school%2C%20she%20was%20staying%20at%20home%20-%20as%20happens%20so%20often%20in%20the%20country's%20rural%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20March%203%2C%20her%20family%20married%20her%20off%20Madesh%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20labourer%20from%20the%20mountain%20village%20of%20Karnataka's%20Kalikuttai.%20Her%20protests%20went%20unheard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wedding%20took%20place%20in%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20to%20her%20hometown%20of%20Thimmathur%2C%20the%20girl%20expressed%20dissatisfaction%20with%20the%20marriage%20again%20and%20refused%20to%20go%20to%20her%20in-laws'%20house.%20She%20also%20voiced%20her%20protests%20to%20her%20parents%20and%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20protests%20fell%20on%20deaf%20ears%20again.%20Madesh%20and%20his%20elder%20brother%20Mallesh%2C%2038%2C%20forcibly%20carried%20off%20the%20girl%20from%20a%20relative's%20house%20to%20Kalikuttai%20village.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnVisuals%20of%20what%20amounts%20to%20a%20kidnapping%20was%20recorded%20on%20cellphone%20by%20onlookers%20and%20uploaded%20on%20social%20media%2C%20where%20it%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20All-Women%20Police%20station%20in%20Denkanikottai%20is%20now%20investigating%20the%20matter.%20A%20formal%20complaint%20has%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20girl's%20grandmother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20police%20arrested%20Madesh%2C%20his%20brother%20Mallesh%2C%20and%20the%20girl's%20mother%20Nagamma.%20Earlier%20today%2C%20two%20more%20arrests%20were%20made%20-%20the%20girl's%20father%20and%20Mallesh'%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECases%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20all%20of%20them%20under%20various%20sections%20pf%20POCSO%20(Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20Act)%20and%20Child%20marriage%20Act.%20All%20of%20them%20face%20two%20years%20in%20jail%20and%20a%20find%20that%20may%20extend%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20is%20now%20living%20with%20her%20grandparents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarriage%20of%20a%20woman%20under%20the%20age%20is%2018%20is%20illegal%20and%20under%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Child%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20and%20is%20considered%20null.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20act%20also%20provides%20punishments%20for%20various%20offences%20for%20allowing%20or%20conducting%20child%20marriages%20between%20minors%20or%20marrying%20minors%20with%20adults.%20Despite%20this%2C%20child%20marriage%20is%20still%20widespread%20across%20the%20nation%2C%20especially%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%C2%A0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20data%20available%20in%202023-%202024%2C%20the%20authorities%20had%20received%20information%20about%20180%20child%20marriages%20in%20Karnataka%3B%20105%20such%20marriages%20were%20prevented%20and%20in%20the%20remaining%2075%20instances%2C%20police%20cases%20were%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741285980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F8a1urqeo_karnataka-child-marriage_625x300_06_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-14-year-old-forcibly-married-physically-carried-off-by-husband-7865209%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20teen%20roughly%20carried%20off%20by%20a%20man%2C%20her%20cries%20and%20shrieks%20carrying%20over%20the%20barren%20fields.%20While%20another%20man%20and%20woman%20follow%2C%20they%20make%20no%20attempt%20to%20come%20to%20her%20aid.%20This%20video%20from%20Karnataka's%20Hosur%20is%20now%20being%20widely%20circulated