ents%2C%20Justice%20Tirthankar%20Ghosh%20also%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20file%20a%20detailed%20report%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruckus%20broke%20out%20within%20the%20university%20campus%20on%20Saturday%20when%20the%20Minister's%20car%20was%20allegedly%20stopped%20after%20it%20entered%20the%20campus%2C%20and%20a%20scuffle%20followed.%20The%20students%20were%20demanding%20immediate%20elections%20for%20the%20university's%20students'%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agitating%20students%20alleged%20that%20while%20Basu%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%20campus%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20protests%2C%20his%20vehicle%20deliberately%20hit%20the%20two%20agitating%20students%2C%20following%20which%20they%20were%20severely%20injured%20and%20had%20to%20be%20hospitalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20protests%2C%20the%20Minister%20received%20minor%20injuries%20and%20fell%20sick.%20He%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20state-run%20S.S.K.M.%20Medical%20College%20%26amp%3B%20Hospital%20and%20was%20discharged%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741284840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fr28mkato_bratya-basu_625x300_02_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjadavpur-university-ruckus-kolkata-police-file-fir-against-west-bengal-minister-bratya-basu-his-driver-tmc-leader-7864766%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kolkata%20Police%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20registered%20FIRs%20against%20West%20Bengal%20Education%20Minister%20Bratya%20Basu%2C%20the%20driver%20of%20his%20vehicle%2C%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Om%20Prakash%20Mishra%20over%20the%20March%201%20ruckus%20within%20the%20campus%20of%20Jadavpur%20University.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjadavpur-university-ruckus-kolkata-police-file-fir-against-west-bengal-minister-bratya-basu-his-driver-tmc-leader-7864766%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jack%20Daniel's%20CEO%20Says%20Canada%20Pulling%20US%20Alcohol%20'Worse%20Than%20Tariff'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20trade%20dispute%20between%20Canada%20and%20the%20US%20has%20escalated%2C%20with%20several%20Canadian%20provinces%20pulling%20American-made%20alcohol%20from%20store%20shelves.%20The%20move%20is%20a%20direct%20response%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20imposition%20of%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Canadian%20goods.%20Lawson%20Whiting%2C%20CEO%20of%20Brown-Forman%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20Jack%20Daniel's%2C%20has%20denounced%20the%20Canadian%20retaliation%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bworse%20than%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdisproportionate%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20US%20levies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20that's%20worse%20than%20a%20tariff%2C%20because%20it's%20literally%20taking%20your%20sales%20away%2C%20completely%20removing%20our%20products%20from%20the%20shelves%2C%26quot%3B%20Whiting%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Liquor%20Control%20Board%20of%20Ontario%20(LCBO)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20alcohol%20buyers%2C%20removed%20US-made%20drinks%20from%20its%20shelves%20on%20Tuesday.%20Ontario%20Premier%20Doug%20Ford%20revealed%20that%20the%20LCBO%20sells%20nearly%20%241%20billion%20worth%20of%20US%20alcohol%20annually%2C%20emphasising%20that%20all%20these%20products%20are%20now%20off%20the%20shelves.%20The%20LCBO's%20exclusive%20wholesaler%20status%20in%20Ontario%20means%20that%20other%20retailers%2C%20bars%2C%20and%20restaurants%20in%20the%20province%20can%20no%20longer%20restock%20US%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20retaliated%20against%20the%20US%20tariffs%20with%20its%20own%2025%25%20levies%20on%20American%20goods%2C%20including%20beer%2C%20spirits%2C%20and%20wine.%20Some%20provinces%2C%20such%20as%20Ontario%20and%20Nova%20Scotia%2C%20have%20taken%20additional%20measures.%20The%20trade%20tensions%20have%20sparked%20a%20nationalist%20sentiment%20among%20Canadians%2C%20with%20some%20opting%20to%20buy%20local%20products%20instead%20of%20US-made%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhiting%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20Canada%20accounts%20for%20only%201%25%20of%20the%20company's%20total%20sales%2C%20making%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20trade%20dispute%20manageable.%20However%2C%20the%20company%20is%20also%20monitoring%20developments%20in%20Mexico%2C%20which%20accounted%20for%207%25%20of%20its%20sales%20in%202024%20and%20has%20also%20been%20affected%20by%20US%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trade%20dispute%20has%20drawn%20strong%20reactions%20from%20Canadian%20leaders.%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20criticised%20the%20US%20tariffs%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20dumb%20thing%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20accused%20President%20Trump%20of%20seeking%20to%20undermine%20the%20Canadian%20economy.%20Canada's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20has%20expressed%20concern%20over%20Trump's%20remarks%20about%20making%20Canada%20the%2051st%20US%20state%2C%20taking%20them%20%26quot%3Bvery%20seriously%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741284480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F19qr5028_lawson-whiting_625x300_06_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjack-daniels-ceo-says-canada-pulling-us-alcohol-worse-than-tariff-7864939%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lawson%20Whiting%2C%20CEO%20of%20Brown-Forman%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20Jack%20Daniel's%2C%20has%20denounced%20the%20Canadian%20retaliation%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bworse%20than%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdisproportionate%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20US%20levies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F