ucial%20for%20us.%20Given%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20tournament%20and%20the%20matches%20ahead%2C%20I%20discussed%20with%20Sunil%20Chhetri%20about%20making%20a%20comeback%20to%20strengthen%20the%20national%20team.%20He%20agreed%2C%20and%20so%20we%20have%20included%20him%20in%20the%20squad.%26quot%3B%20Since%20his%20retirement%2C%20he%20had%20continued%20playing%20for%20Bengaluru%20FC%20in%20the%20Indian%20Super%20League.%20He%20has%20so%20far%20scored%2012%20goals%20from%2023%20matches%20this%20season%20to%20become%20its%20highest%20Indian%20goal-scorer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShillong's%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Stadium%20will%20host%20the%20Indian%20senior%20men's%20team's%20two%20matches%20that%20they%20will%20play%20during%20the%20FIFA%20international%20window%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20been%20placed%20in%20a%20qualifying%20group%20alongside%20Bangladesh%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20and%20Singapore%20for%20the%20Asian%20Cup.%20In%20the%20tournament's%20previous%20edition%2C%20India%20had%20a%20disappointing%20run%2C%20failing%20to%20progress%20past%20the%20group%20stage%20after%20losing%20all%20their%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%2026-member%20squad%20for%20March%202025%20FIFA%20International%20Window%3A%20Goalkeepers%3A%20Amrinder%20Singh%2C%20Gurmeet%20Singh%2C%20Vishal%20Kaith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefenders%3A%20Asish%20Rai%2C%20Boris%20Singh%20Thangjam%2C%20Chinglensana%20Singh%20Konsham%2C%20Hmingthanmawia%2C%20Mehtab%20Singh%2C%20Rahul%20Bheke%2C%20Roshan%20Singh%2C%20Sandesh%20Jhingan%2C%20Subhasish%20Bose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMidfielders%3A%20Ashique%20Kuruniyan%2C%20Ayush%20Dev%20Chhetri%2C%20Brandon%20Fernandes%2C%20Brison%20Fernandes%2C%20Jeakson%20Singh%20Thounaojam%2C%20Lalengmawia%2C%20Liston%20Colaco%2C%20Mahesh%20Singh%20Naorem%2C%20Suresh%20Singh%20Wangjam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForwards%3A%20Sunil%20Chhetri%2C%20Farukh%20Choudhary%2C%20Irfan%20Yadwad%2C%20Lallianzuala%20Chhangte%2C%20Manvir%20Singh%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(